ticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَكَانَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And (it) is</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَمْرًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a matter</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَّقْضِيًّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">decreed.'"</span></span></span> <a href="#!/quran-wordbyword/19:21" class="ayahNumber" data-verse="2271"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>21<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></a></p>
